      <li><a href="/wiki/core/concepts/layout-overview/">Layout System</a> - Layout concepts and philosophy</li>
      <li><a href="/wiki/core/concepts/state-management/">State Management</a> - Managing application state</li>
      <li><a href="/wiki/core/concepts/event-system/">Event System</a> - Event handling architecture</li>
