    <h2>Face Model</h2>
    <p>The face model is the foundation of Vista's UI system. Faces are the basic building blocks that represent UI elements with properties, state, and behavior.</p>

    <h2>Event System</h2>
    <p>Vista provides a comprehensive event system that allows you to respond to user interactions, from simple clicks to complex gestures.</p>

